e there are existing tabs already. Also, I’m considering whether to include nativeTest—maybe the plugin could handle that configuration for me. It might be helpful to search through other build.gradle files for reference to see how they manage similar setups. Let’s see what this yields!", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_02928e0d39233fc60169f891f4d69c8192a7a3b5b9d7586bde\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp-JID3gckemXXEeRdC65fMTn_ZFG3B20Rm1_EgDlKZ7WUOVkjzwpJRWpt69QMzuJCHBtV8ni8pi5VrZl_bI6DtiZ2Nmt7egCSQrMkzokBXuFmmTpA6VoeADkaG0yMqt3yCY2fX4E99BzD2SVypja3FIeu2qdZB2YZUfIEOUUHht_F-7Ba2QhO0n32YYOE-lKJu-7l-r3sCVHKxRNTT_r1ZRgzvJLHfPyQ_bqTgM8wkryH7ePbWUCLi-qiGhhOcmGUD9KsXWZc5r-JIMEAxhlOpd8Wm_CJ9CjRDTZDbfpEXk9nsBOrwWaJxl8OoavhCxNhZrwf8c544ziNsTHvWzKcUVyG0IZVAuDwM6-kZFVoq8-syjFfeCeUlqO-eCy6ilFMT_HbQXDIEfpXdLnTZGZrrEH3wa-nxQUElqlmHSF6eRQTrxOLermKFF1zESH5xF09ePWxQR6BxVl0qWjkQva31WRjDIXmqhRC4U_knYkkv3qC0dQWKjhiVoYtMhDP1_APPPmFNcYhlYfnf-5rz4_wBXIsEghs_iltUW4bG16hJReHfc2VlXQrz_vA2LZQxUkym_nBc5WD1QdcLKs6YUnnqRjC44kP1BWSkUt6Jj6Cmv-qdkbnInc9d61BQpEfOCStZozq1rmoiLxtqp5KKknuePo6RfsfPsXuUbzBMhIrCqaxzwcIdlBrZ0RVh0cokTjl270ruoStCrQiiKMULTACvYOYuIoMIxJWc9xpgOzEdBYv72Bj4Z4ZtVkI3JicLEo2zkwb1ggIxOjkN7uM1D1zjVVNylA67DG8ETktNFA9D5f3BpGgwRPFy6lYyNdD5peiMyb2Eggh6_SQVGYYg2Oh0O23zFJJ6gQ6IXwRFhGv6Y4puj6AyP45USeStEASmXXsW-4KKKZ6A4Xj-RfH-FFAJ9tXp8VlxyC0sdcMWPZiY4dpOgSDSMJWt1krprGw83zMpoh8AJJkeCxGYcH0JMDDV7NboSo5oJPA2yqVEF6iX4k3S01TPtFAs7OgI8R6NKVBbkPat9e-7w_Ew0nn4ZUDo7FJDG3EXrT-da7_q7-pxHSwxh8JoXlkKukqhSN30I3G5TUwxwbm9eZqFKsu9j9idDzCpkOrKfsLJ1l5PkxU2A45hUMDWrPvUH1_yzTYf8GT8o3Mt466ZQobbIiumzCFzIDdF_u1MQPVtT0zEQ8RtMM19sPuO7Lg3iXgdFI06yqXTB4-LJn-jpC_uKd352fO3kADLhIMOGpwRjQR8sHEdgKNc9JaUT-FldofvGMxEFjhj1Ll3eGAIGzq0dG9QEEqM5Zo623Gag9eqsIFDVgYb91zyznw1yIyTOsF4BuGKfYoikt4kkwjiKPUOd4og8xQojPR3zxSjg6UefXNin_ifMff1btQrCXmagwgPVEA2cQsn-8ZbuBb6YKeq3bzQXp7okK-1E5sjh_t4HVlSfE5re48ZcWFUYrUrRi6BZCbMXyv6ETiV0q-YfLZa2ELyixfistDdhZ88zxtbWawY_cb9vd42_i3R49Oa7HhF2hj3zohPvyJMSP3jFta7zpwv7lYyPWG0JMgRuO